{"tid":2362952,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Telegram 始創人叫大家盡快棄 iOS 轉 Android，Apple 比 Google 更危險","createTime":"2021-01-12T00:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T15:17:32.000Z","uid":156133,"like":115,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"8226a9a5af795e4d01b3926a4dfb5c9eb69b8875","tid":2362952,"uid":156133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T00:05:06.000Z","msg":"一場美國總統選舉，帶出一場場科技界的腥風血雨，大家應該重新考慮，你的「自由」是否仍然自由。最近 Apple 及 Google 指 Parler 違反了他們的政策，沒有對平台上的言論進行監管，決定把 Parler 應用程式從 App Store 及 Play Store 下架。對於一個應用程式而言，這手法明顯是一場「圍剿」。<br />\n<br />\nTelegram 始創人 Pavel Durov 對此曾深有感觸，為此 Pavel Durov 對大家發出呼籲「請大家盡快由 iOS 轉換至 Android 系統」。<br />\n<br />\nPavel Durov 認為 Apple 及 Google 兩大巨頭壟斷了整個移動系統市場，不過 Apple 比 Google 更危險，因為 Apple 是完全控制了大家可以用什麼 Apps (除非你越獄)，而 Android 至少可以選擇下載 APK 方式安裝 Apps，這就是他希望大家放棄 iOS 轉會 Android 的原因。<br />\n<br />\nApple 壟斷市場問題日益嚴重，近年對於壟斷的官司不斷，Apple 的壟斷應該值得大家重視。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://qooah.com/2021/01/11/the-founder-of-telegram-tells-everyone-to-abandon-ios-to-android-as-soon-as-possible/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2021%2F01%2F11%2Fthe-founder-of-telegram-tells-everyone-to-abandon-ios-to-android-as-soon-as-possible%2F&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=c5b1a1a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2021/01/11/the-founder-of-telegram-tells-everyone-to-abandon-ios-to-android-as-soon-as-possible/</a>"},{"pid":"7167aaadd6bffddf1e316f8a0f39a4d30894481c","tid":2362952,"uid":196924,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T00:44:32.000Z","msg":"暫時Android仲係可以custom ROM<br />\n好似華為咁，被封殺都仲可以用到"},{"pid":"2e77dfa501e310828fd6a46d49bc60fcc4d188dc","tid":2362952,"uid":288304,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T00:50:56.000Z","msg":"老老實實，兩面都要搞個正常的換機app就真<br />\n<br />\n哩D真係要EU出手"},{"pid":"eddd3a1e48adb882d9ddc72e6f885854f1c65445","tid":2362952,"uid":11719,"like":18,"dislike":81,"score":-6